code: export class Randomizer{static getRandomNumber(count){return Math.floor(Math.random()*count);}static getRandomElement(elements){return elements[this.getRandomNumber(elements.length)];}static getRandomElements(elements,count){const result=new Array(count);let len=elements.length;const taken=new Array(len);while(count--){var x=this.getRandomNumber(len);result[count]=elements[x in taken?taken[x]:x];taken[x]=--len in taken?taken[len]:len;}return result;}}
